Direct Known Subclasses:
AmountParser, ListParser, MapParser, PairParser, SetParser
public abstract class TypeParameterizedParser<T>
extends BaseParser<T>

Parser that makes implementation of parsers for parameterized types simpler. This only works for top-level parameters. Behavior is undefined for nested parameterized types. For example, this will handle Map<String, Integer> fine but will not handle Map<String, List<String>.
